      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Honey Garlic Glazed Salmon. Built in the way Chinese home kitchens cook: fast at the wok, balance at the bowl. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A weeknight-friendly recipe: most of the work is the prep, and the cooking takes care of itself.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
